thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by An Jan Teng

author: An Jan Teng
title: An Jan Teng
text:
The staffs are helpful. Although I got my car after hour, and return my car after hours too, didn't see any staff in my nz honeymoon at all.
The only thing I am not satisify is the car Omega gave my is a little old, and the back space is limited. The rent number is compare a little expensive more than ACE south island rental. (I also rent a car in South Island, to ACE rental, they gave us a bigger back space Coralla, much cheaper and newer.)
